caption_original: Until recently, breweries in the Maritimes depended on imported barley and hops. Our researchers have been working with the Atlantic Grains Council and local craft beer makers in the Maritimes to develop varieties of barley and hops suited to the region's growing conditions. These new varieties will help make #StPatricksDay suds more local.
